


polar(1)                       Scilab Function                       polar(1)






NAME
  polar - polar form

CALLING SEQUENCE
  [Ro,Theta]=polar(A)

PARAMETERS
  A    : real or complex square matrix
  Ro, Theta
       : real matrices

DESCRIPTION
  [Ro,Theta]=polar(A) returns the polar form of A i.e.:
  A=Ro*exp(%i*Theta) Ro symmetric >=0 and Theta hermitian >=0.

